(26, 'story', NULL, 3, '迷你小说《三军集结败走东濠涌 东鸣轩欲求一鸣惊人》之二', 1, '2015-04-22', '<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;">当晚，DMX营大排数十筵席，款待“被俘”将士及亲属，并开出极之优惠条款，声称只要将士们归顺本营，一律以友相待。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;">被俘将士见救兵罕至，“会师大计”已然无望，逐纷纷于筵席上大快朵颐后归顺DMX营，签署“城下之盟”者不少于百人。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;">盛宴后仅数日，三军中百余将士顿成娘子军“囊中宝”。娘子军主帅正苦于营中无兵，此番秒杀逆袭，更是不亚于囊中探物“执到宝”，DMX营瞬间得以壮大！昔日DMX营河飞水静，营中“见将不见兵”，士卒寥寥无几，几近空城！但今日城头上已是巨幅旗帜飘扬、高朋满座、人来人往，熙熙攘攘矣！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;">数日后，“三军”欲重整旗鼓，意欲反扑，但奈何14号一役已是损兵折将，元气大伤，队伍已然难带矣！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;"></span>', '2015-05-14 15:08:06'),
