(55, 'story', NULL, 1, '迷你小说《三军集结败走东濠涌 东鸣轩欲求一鸣惊人》之四', 1, '2015-04-24', '<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;">然BB营在城外涌边已苦撑近3年，虽“火器”（商铺硬件）了得，一时无人能敌，奈何长江后浪摧（是摧毁的摧不是推）前浪，在当今时代，“火器”日新月异，已非罕见之物，无出其右者日众，“火器”犀利也已非战场之优势；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;">君不见，除距BB营789米“火器”了得的DMX营外，更近的474米处也有一个枕戈待旦、坐拥5层商铺的硕大军营，名曰“金濠汇”营吗？可见城中不缺“火器”，惟缺将士兵马入驻矣！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;">BB营苏州过后的战略战术技不如人，现在落得个功不成，名不就，身难退的境地。正是：人算不如天算，螳螂捕蝉，当小心黄雀在后！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;">各位看官，欲知三军败走东涌后战况如何发展，“BB”又会否沦为城外涌边“弃婴”？且听下半年出版的《下回分解之XXXXXXXXX &nbsp; XXXXXXXXX》，当可“知秋看一叶”矣！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style="color:#333333;font-family:''Century Gothic'', ''Microsoft yahei'';font-size:medium;line-height:22.8571434020996px;background-color:#F5F5F5;"></span>', '2015-05-14 15:08:06'),
