(75, 'activity', NULL, 33, '2015中国国际钱币（广州）展销会完满收宫', 1, '2015-07-26', '<p>\r\n	由中国收藏家协会主办，广银阁、首席收藏、华艺国际联合承办的2015中国国际钱币（广州）展销会，于今天7月26日在广州东方文德艺术品交易中心隆重闭幕，本次大会在广州成功举办，获得了全球各地近百余家钱币机构、币商、藏家等的大力支持。东鸣轩收藏品中心参加了今次为期三天的展销活动，期间宣传团队在郭帅的带领下向广大商家及客户成功推广东鸣轩收藏中心，在大家的努力下为东鸣轩带来了不错的口碑，赢得众多潜在客户，为打造成功辉煌的东鸣轩打下坚实的基础。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	郭帅带领下的精英团队\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20150803/20150803062134_24370.jpg" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	会场一角\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20150803/20150803062155_78400.jpg" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6000003814697px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">东鸣轩展位现场</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20150803/20150803064445_61597.jpg" alt="" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6000003814697px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">展会期间的礼品得到众多东鸣轩商家的大力支持，工作人员为大会参加者准备礼物</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20150803/20150803064534_62698.jpg" alt="" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6000003814697px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">来自台湾的探极杂志有机会成为东鸣轩的合作伙伴</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20150803/20150803064628_35092.jpg" alt="" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6000003814697px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">华艺拍卖现场</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/2015