(81, 'activity', NULL, 29, '第一套人民币大系---《票券概述》内部参考资料，将于五月中旬开放预约', 1, '2017-05-10', '<p>\r\n	<img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20150817/20150817040051_53970.jpg" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="line-height:23.2727279663086px;">2015.8.15至2015.9.15</span><strong><span style="color:#FF0000;">东鸣轩收藏品中心</span></strong><span style="line-height:23.2727279663086px;">为纪念中国抗日战争胜利和世界反法西斯战争胜利70周年联合</span><strong>广东省收藏家协会军品专业委员会、功勋阁历史文化收藏馆、华侨历史文献档案馆举办</strong><span style="line-height:23.2727279663086px;">“</span><span style="line-height:23.2727279663086px;color:#FF0000;"><strong>抗战文物展</strong></span><span style="line-height:23.2727279663086px;">”即将开幕，敬请留意！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n<strong><span style="font-size:20px;"> </span></strong>抗日战争胜利纪念日是第二次世界大战太平洋战场中，日本投降从而战争结束的日期及其后每年的纪念日。1945年9月2日，参加对日作战的同盟国代表接受日本投降签字仪式在停泊于日本东京湾的美军军舰“密苏里”号上举行。日本代表在无条件投降书上签字，中、美、英、苏等9国代表相继签字。至此，中国抗日战争胜利结束，世界反法西斯战争也落下帷幕。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	由于时差关系，美国的“对日战争胜利纪念日”为9月2日。中国的“抗日战争胜利纪念日”定于9月3日。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong><span>“</span><span><strong>抗战文物展</strong></span><span>”预展，部份展品先睹为快</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong><span><strong><span>展会主办方，东鸣轩收藏品中心大门</span></strong><br />\r\n</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20150817/20150817040202_20233.jpg" alt="" /> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span><span><strong><span style="font-size:16px;">“</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>抗战文物展</strong></span><span style="font-size:16px;">”现场</span></strong></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:16px;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/attached/image/20150817/20150817040756_96778.jpg" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040502_96297.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040503_12230.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040505_19684.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040505_90126.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040506_50970.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040506_78573.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040509_22205.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040510_74363.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040512_13938.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040512_47955.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040514_29964.jpg" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	更多精彩内容敬请亲临现场参观，还有精美纪念邮资封赠送，先到先得！\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong><br />\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong>《终战诏书》原件</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size:16px;color:#444444;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong>日本裕仁天皇终战诏书</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040639_99151.jpg" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040640_19299.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040641_14680.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040644_98536.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040647_47795.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040648_82619.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040649_78483.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040651_36784.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040653_28196.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040657_52646.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040700_57125.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040703_81246.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040706_19687.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20150817/20150817040709_86632.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/dmx/Public/kindeditor/php/../atta