区、钱庄票、新中国（一、二、三、套）号码币、封签、金银币、机制币、铜元、方孔钱<br />\r\n3、卡类：全国各省田川卡、200卡、lC卡、国卡，银行卡、交通卡、地铁卡等</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">4、征集数量:20框</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="color:#FF0000;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;">二、征集要求：</span></strong></span><span style="font-family:宋体;"><br />\r\n1、要求展品为真品。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">2、所有展品交到组委会后，由组委会鉴定小组鉴定后，组委会统一交给主办方布展，展品可以标价出售，待展览结束后，由出品方交给买家。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">3、展品征集截止时间：</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;text-indent:24px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">2015年11月1日</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#FF0000;">三、<strong>组委会联系电话：</strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">1、东鸣轩收藏品中心活动负责人：秦淮13825039636</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">2、广东省收藏家协会邮币卡专业委员会主任：陈志军13332820729</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">3、广东省集币协会广州分会会长：李志超13711560068</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">4、广州卡友俱乐部：张检13539815035</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong><span style="color:#FF0000;font-family:宋体;">东鸣轩2015邮币卡秋季博览会组委会</span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n		<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong><span style="color:#FF0000;">2015-10-15</span></strong></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n<br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#3E3E3E;font-family:''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:宋体;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>', '2015-10-17 01:33:42'),
